title: Ranks were reset?
body: I thought the ranked season ends in November, why did ranks reset?

replies.body: Profiles are showing as placement while we undergo maintenance, so this is just a display issue.  Updates will be provided on the [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page.  Everything will appear as normal once this is over!

Ranks have not reset. Riot is currently performing maintenance, and during this time they have disabled the Leagues system, so you will be unable to view your rank or ranked stats. This is just visual, though, until the maintenance is over. Ranked games will still count as normal.
I was at 94 lp and won a game. Will promo games count regarding that?
